\r\n<v:textbox style="width:720px;height:125px;" inset="0,0,0,0">\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="height:125px;font-size:14px;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Sans-Serif;width:720px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;"><tr>\r\n<td style="height:125px;color:#ffffff;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Sans-Serif;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">\r\n    <p style="background-color:transparent;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:14px;">Brian Tracy''s</p>\r\n    <p style="background-color:transparent;color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold;font-size:40px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Success Newsletter</p>\r\n    <p style="background-color:transparent;color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;padding-bottom:14px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:4px;">For Personal Achievement and Time Management</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="vertical-align:bottom;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">\r\n    <img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/email/brian-tracy.png" alt="" height="110" width="143" />\r\n</td>\r\n</tr></table>\r\n</v:textbox>\r\n</v:rect>\r\n</div>\r\n<style type="text/css">/*<![endif]-->\r\n<div id="topbarwrap" class="outhide" style="background-color:#4b2659;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">\r\n<div id="topbar" style=''background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-webkit-background-size:cover;background:#4b2659 url("http://www.briantracy.com/files/email/per-top1.jpg") repeat-x;''>\r\n<div id="header" style="position:relative;color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div id="bt1" style="color:#ffffff;padding-top:17px;font-size:16px;">Brian Tracy''s</div>\r\n<div id="bt2" style="color:#ffffff;line-height:100%;margin-top:7px;font-weight:bold;font-size:25px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Success Newsletter</div>\r\n<div id="bt3" style="color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:15px;padding-top:7px;font-size:14px;">For Personal Achievement and Time Management</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding-left:20px;vertical-align:bottom;">\r\n<div id="bt4" style="overflow:hidden;max-height:1px;width:1px;height:1px;display:none;"><img id="btimg" src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/email/brian-tracy.png" alt="" height="1" width="1" style="width:1px;max-height:1px;height:1px;display:none;" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr></table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="line" style="background-color:#c2c2c2;height:2px;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--[if gte mso 9]>*/</style><![endif]-->\r\n<div id="top-nav" style="overflow:hidden;max-height:1px;height:1px;display:none;">\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151461&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151462&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151463&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151464&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151465&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151466&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div id="main" style="background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:16px;">\r\n<p>Hi jul1441434n,&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>First off, I wanted to make sure you claimed your free special report the other day.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Remember, it''s called "Discovering Your Talents,&rdquo; and it&rsquo;s designed to give you all the information you need to earn higher rewards on your energy invested &ndash; resulting in a more satisfying, more enjoyable life.</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151467&amp;ebr=170715503">You can still claim your copy here.</a></p>\r\n<p>Now, let&rsquo;s get to today''s exciting news: I&rsquo;ve had such a great response from the people who read the &ldquo;Discovering Your Talents&rdquo; report &ndash; they&rsquo;re freshly inspired to reveal their talents and unlock their full potential.</p>\r\n<p>Many of those messages of thanks and excitement have also included a common question: &ldquo;How do I discover what I am REALLY meant to do with my life?&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>It happens so often...you think about doing one thing, and the next thing you know you''re off doing something completely different.</p>\r\n<p><strong>It''s NOT your fault. We all start out the same that way.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Very few of us know what we want to do when we grow up.</p>\r\n<p>I can tell you I certainly fell into this category...That is, until I discovered a life-altering secret.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What makes some people more successful than others is their ability to have a clear vision of who they are and what talents they bring to the table.</strong></p>\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s why &ldquo;clarity&rdquo; is one of my favorite words.</p>\r\n<p>It helps people discover what I call the "music inside of them" and it''s one of the most important elements in getting what you want in life and business.</p>\r\n<p>With clarity comes a sense of peace and calming, as you realize who you were meant to be and what you were meant to do.</p>\r\n<p><strong>But how do you gain that clarity &ndash; the focus that drives you toward attainment of all your most important goals?</strong></p>\r\n<p>That''s what I reveal in the FREE video I just released.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151468&amp;ebr=170715503">Grab your FREE video here.</a></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151469&amp;ebr=170715503"><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/Newsletters/POC%20Video%20Screen%20Shot.png" alt="" width="250" height="165" /></a></p>\r\n<p>To your success,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" width="216" height="86" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n<p>P.S. Don''t waste another minute of your life feeling stagnant.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151470&amp;ebr=170715503">Learn how to achieve clarity today.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="bottom-nav" style="overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:10px;">\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151471&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151472&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151473&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151474&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151475&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=151476&amp;ebr=170715503" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div> \r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>\r\n<td id="footer" style="color:#222222;font-size:14px;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Sans-Serif;background-color:#d9d9d9;padding-bottom:14px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:14px;">\r\n<p class="ftitle" style="margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;font-weight:bold;padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Change Your Email</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;"><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/ce.aspx?c=XlEUAIoOAAAC" style="color:#1d3c5a;">Update your email address</a>.</p>\r\n<p class="ftitle" style="margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;font-weight:bold;padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Get Involved!</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;"><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/Newsletters/twitter.png" alt="twitter" title="Twitter" height="15" width="15" />  \r\nFollow me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=183358&amp;ebr=170715503" style="color:#1d3c5a;">Twitter</a>.<br /><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/Newsletters/facebook.png" alt="Facebook" title="Facebook" height="15" width="15" />  \r\nBecome a fan on\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=183359&amp;ebr=170715503" style="color:#1d3c5a;">Facebook</a>.<br /><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/Newsletters/linkedin.png" alt="LinkedIn" title="LinkedIn" height="15" width="15" />  \r\nConnect with me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=183360&amp;ebr=170715503" style="color:#1d3c5a;">\r\nLinkedIn</a><br /><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/Newsletters/youtube.png" alt="YouTube" title="YouTube" height="15" width="15" />  \r\nWatch me on <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sb