y.com/s.aspx?c=XlEUAIoOAAAC" style="color:#1d3c5a;"></a> \r\n| \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=183364&amp;ebr=170715503" style="color:#1d3c5a;">Privacy Policy</a></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;">', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '2014-07-05 14:45:03', '2014-07-05 14:45:03', 'Active'),
(133, 'JUL1441434N', 'JUL1441434N140705150002', 'child', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', 0, 'NO', 'Brian Tracy', 'What the best investors are buying right now [Free Training]', 'Brian Tracy', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', 'NO', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN">\r\n<html>\r\n	<head>\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en-us">\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">\r\n	<title>A Message From Brian Tracy</title>\r\n	</head>\r\n	<body><div style=''height:2px;''><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/images/btis170729728.gif" width="10" height="2" alt=""></div>\r\n		<style type="text/css">\r\n	p {margin-bottom: 1em;}\r\n\r\n			.NLTitle {font-weight: normal; font-size: 16pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial;}\r\n			.NLSubtitle {font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: none;}\r\n			.NLAuthor {font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic;}\r\n		</style>\r\n		\r\n		<span style="color: #222222; font-weight:normal; font-size:12pt; font-family: Arial;">\r\n\r\n		<p>Hi&nbsp;jul1441434n,</p>\r\n<p>When it comes to investing, we want to grow our money with the highest return and lowest risk possible in a world without obvious places to put the money safely.</p>\r\n<p>And we want to do it without a lot of work, right?&nbsp; While there are no shortcuts to getting rich, there are smarter ways to go about it.</p>\r\n<p>Consider this&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>How hard do you think investing would be if Warren Buffett told you what stocks he&rsquo;s buying and how much you should pay?&nbsp; Not so hard, right?&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>My good friend Phil Town is a New York Times Best-Selling Author and Investment Expert.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;In fact, he actually taught me how to get the most successful investors in the world to show me what they&rsquo;re buying into, and tell me what I <em>should be</em> buying into.</p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re not familiar with Phil Town, he&rsquo;s spoken on stages across the world and has appeared on CNBC and MSNBC and Fox to educate others on how to invest like the PROS do.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>And he can do the same for you (even if you&rsquo;ve never made a single investment in your LIFE!)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191799&amp;ebr=170729728">Go here now for FREE Expert investing advice</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Professional investors generally receive an upwards of 20% to 30% annual return on their investments, using the SAME principals Phil will teach you absolutely FREE.</p>\r\n<p>No questions asked, no selling WHATSOEVER.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191800&amp;ebr=170729728">Want to know how Warren Buffet does it? Find out now</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>To your success,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n<p>P.S. Here''s what some of Phil''s students are saying...</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>&ldquo;This education has been the best step I have taken in my life.&rdquo;</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>--Greg Nowicki, January 7<sup>th</sup>, 2014</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>&ldquo;We have to say, Phil totally changed our view of investing by providing insights into the investing world that were unknown to us before.&nbsp; We are very grateful to the folks at Rule One Investing for giving us the skills we need to change our financial future.&rdquo;</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>-- Sandi Wheeler and Tom DeMeo, January 6<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;2014</p>\r\n\r\n		</span>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><strong>Get Involved!</strong><br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/twitter.gif" alt="twitter" title="Twitter" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nFollow me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191801&amp;ebr=170729728" style="color:#1d3c5a">Twitter</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/facebook.gif" alt="Facebook" title="Facebook" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nBecome a fan on\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191802&amp;ebr=170729728" style="color:#1d3c5a">Facebook</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/linkedin.gif" alt="LinkedIn" title="LinkedIn" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nConnect with me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191803&amp;ebr=170729728" style="color:#1d3c5a">LinkedIn</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/youtube.gif" alt="YouTube" title="YouTube" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nWatch me on <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191804&amp;ebr=170729728" style="color:#1d3c5a">Youtube</a>.<br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/blog.gif" alt="Blog" title="Blog" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; Check out my <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191805&amp;ebr=170729728" style="color:#1d3c5a">Blog</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n		<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><br /><br /><a style="color: #1d3c5a;" href="https://www.briantracy.com/s.aspx?c=XlEUALoSAAAC"> </a> <a style="color: #1d3c5a;" href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=191806&amp;ebr=170729728">Privacy Policy</a> &copy; 2000-2014, Brian Tracy International. All Rights Reserved.</p>\r\n\r\n	</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '2014-07-05 15:00:02', '2014-07-05 15:00:02', 'Active'),
