(138, 'JUL1441434N', 'JUL1441434N140707234502', 'child', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', 0, 'NO', 'Brian Tracy', 'What my Investment Expert said that SHOCKED me [new video]', 'Brian Tracy', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', 'NO', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN">\r\n<html>\r\n	<head>\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en-us">\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">\r\n	<title>A Message From Brian Tracy</title>\r\n	</head>\r\n	<body><div style=''height:2px;''><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/images/btis171480007.gif" width="10" height="2" alt=""></div>\r\n		<style type="text/css">\r\n	p {margin-bottom: 1em;}\r\n\r\n			.NLTitle {font-weight: normal; font-size: 16pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial;}\r\n			.NLSubtitle {font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: none;}\r\n			.NLAuthor {font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic;}\r\n		</style>\r\n		\r\n		<span style="color: #222222; font-weight:normal; font-size:12pt; font-family: Arial;">\r\n\r\n		<p>jul1441434n,</p>\r\n<p>I was talking to my good friend, NY Times #1 Best-Selling Author and Investment Expert, Phil Town, just the other day and he raised some questions that completely shocked me.</p>\r\n<p><strong>When it comes to your financial investments, do you know who&rsquo;s handling your money, where it&rsquo;s being placed and WHY?</strong></p>\r\n<p>If not, you might want to ask yourself THIS question&hellip;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Who&rsquo;s making more money, you or your financial advisor?</strong></p>\r\n<p>If you don&rsquo;t know the answers to these questions, and you want to make sure you are protecting yourself and your financial assets&hellip;</p>\r\n<p><strong><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192306&amp;ebr=171480007">Watch this video NOW.</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>The truth is, if you don&rsquo;t understand the decisions your advisors are making with YOUR money&hellip;then they could be making costly choices at your expense.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192307&amp;ebr=171480007">Click here to find out if your financial future is in jeopardy.</a>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>The answer just might SHOCK you.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>To your success,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n\r\n		</span>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><strong>Get Involved!</strong><br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/twitter.gif" alt="twitter" title="Twitter" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nFollow me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192308&amp;ebr=171480007" style="color:#1d3c5a">Twitter</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/facebook.gif" alt="Facebook" title="Facebook" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nBecome a fan on\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192309&amp;ebr=171480007" style="color:#1d3c5a">Facebook</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/linkedin.gif" alt="LinkedIn" title="LinkedIn" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nConnect with me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192310&amp;ebr=171480007" style="color:#1d3c5a">LinkedIn</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/youtube.gif" alt="YouTube" title="YouTube" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nWatch me on <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192311&amp;ebr=171480007" style="color:#1d3c5a">Youtube</a>.<br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/blog.gif" alt="Blog" title="Blog" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; Check out my <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192312&amp;ebr=171480007" style="color:#1d3c5a">Blog</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n		<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><br /><br /><a style="color: #1d3c5a;" href="https://www.briantracy.com/s.aspx?c=XlEUANESAAAC"> </a> <a style="color: #1d3c5a;" href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=192313&amp;ebr=171480007">Privacy Policy</a> &copy; 2000-2014, Brian Tracy International. All Rights Reserved.</p>\r\n\r\n	</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '2014-07-07 23:45:02', '2014-07-07 23:45:02', 'Active');
