\r\n<p><strong><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=195491&amp;ebr=177150013">Get HUGE discounts today.</a></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>As a reminder, the Summer Sale features life-changing products in 5 categories:</strong></p>\r\n<ol start="1">\r\n<li><strong>Personal Development</strong>-- From harnessing the mindset for success to enjoying life as an adventure, these courses guide you in getting the most out of every moment, no matter what.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sales Success--</strong>Whether you''re selling against lower-priced competition, or you need help with closing, these products give you what you need to succeed, period.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Business Success--</strong>I''ve hand-selected the products in this category to help you maximize your earning potential, get promoted faster, and create your own financial security and abundance.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Time Management--</strong>&nbsp;When you implement the proven techniques and strategies I reveal in this category, you''ll feel like you''ve added hours to your day, while checking off everything on your to-do list!</li>\r\n<li><strong>Leadership--</strong>As a manager, your ability to succeed depends on your ability to create successful teams. Here, you discover everything you need to know to build a strong, efficient team that propels you to success.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=195492&amp;ebr=177150013">Check out my 2014 Summer Sale now.</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To big summer savings,</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=195493&amp;ebr=177150013"><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" width="216" height="86" /></a><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n		</span>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><strong>Get Involved!</strong><br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/con