(205, 'JUL1472418N', 'JUL1472418N140728101112', 'child', 'rich@strategicprofits.com', 0, 'NO', 'Rich Schefren', 'The Profit Vault awaits you...', 'Rich Schefren', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 'Rich Schefren', 'NO', 'rich@strategicprofits.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head><body>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"><img alt="Message from Rich" height="129" src="https://schefren.infusionsoft.com/Download?Id=763715" title="Message from Rich" width="430" />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHey Knewdog,\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat did you think after reading through the last part\r\n<br />\r\nof the Manifesto series... The Final Chapter?\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI hope it opened your eyes to what it takes to build a\r\n<br />\r\nmega-business. You can use the same strategies to \r\n<br />\r\ngrow\r\nyour business long before you reach the million \r\n<br />\r\ndollar\r\nmark.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI''d like to know what you thought, so head over to \r\n<br />\r\nthe\r\nblog and share your comments with me and our \r\n<br />\r\nreaders\r\nhere...\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.strategicprofits.com/strategy/finalchapter/">www.strategicprofits.com/strategy/finalchapter/</a>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNow I''ve got something really special for you.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou''ve just read the same reports that rocked the\r\n<br />\r\nInternet business world. They helped well over \r\n<br />\r\n100,000\r\npeople move forward in a profitable \r\n<br />\r\ndirection. And\r\nrealize their dreams of building a \r\n<br />\r\nsuccessful online\r\nbusiness.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee, when I wrote &quot;The Manifesto&quot; series, I was just\r\n<br />\r\ngetting started...\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNext, I released a series of business-building videos\r\n<br />\r\nthat generated the same flood of comments and \r\n<br />\r\npraise.\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore importantly, "From Startup to Freedom&quot; and \r\n<br />\r\n