r=179852044" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div id="main" style="background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:16px;">\r\n<p>Hi jul1441434n,</p>\r\n<p>By now, you&rsquo;ve hopefully had a chance to check out my special gifts, &ldquo;Getting Your Ideas Across,&rdquo; &ldquo;Planning and Preparation Made Simple,&rdquo; and &ldquo;Start Strong With Any Audience.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135919&amp;ebr=179852044">If not, get them all here.</a></p>\r\n<p>For some of you, those gifts will be enough to launch your communication skills to new heights, and I hope you enjoy the life transformation that is just beginning.</p>\r\n<p>For others, though, they were just the tip of the iceberg. They ignited a spark, and you&rsquo;re ready to let it burn &ndash; because you understand that your ability to communicate determines 85% of your success.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For you, I&rsquo;ve developed a brand-new offering, &ldquo;The Power of Effective Communication.&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135920&amp;ebr=179852044">Skip the reading and get the details here.</a></p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;The Power of Effective Communication&rdquo; comprises 6 of my best-selling products (3 DVDs, 2 CDs and a hard cover book) on the topic, as well as 2 brand new products &ndash; a 12-page PDF report and an online video.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135921&amp;ebr=179852044"><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/effcomm/assets/img/effcomm.jpg" alt="" width="190" height="156" /></a></p>\r\n<p>You get absolutely everything you need to know about communicating effectively, so you can transform every aspect of your life. We start with the basics and continue on to secrets of the masters.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Here&rsquo;s what you get when you order &ldquo;The Power of Effective Communication&rdquo;:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>How to Prepare a Powerful Presentation DVD plus notes</li>\r\n<li>How to Deliver a Winning Presentation DVD plus notes</li>\r\n<li>How to Talk &ndash; Secrets of Great Communicators DVD plus notes</li>\r\n<li>Speak on Your Feet CD</li>\r\n<li>Communicate With Power CD</li>\r\n<li>Speak to Win hard cover book</li>\r\n<li>Motivational Leadership PDF report</li>\r\n<li>Mastering the Skills of Public Speaking online video</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Life belongs to those who take action &ndash; and when you combine action with effective communication, you&rsquo;re unstoppable.</p>\r\n<p>If you''re ready to become unstoppable, get &ldquo;The Power of Effective Communication" today.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135922&amp;ebr=179852044">Order it here.</a></p>\r\n<p>To your success through communication,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n<p>P.S. This is your last chance to get my free gifts, so download them right away,<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135923&amp;ebr=179852044"> here.</a></p>\r\n<p>P.P.S. Because all the items in &ldquo;The Power of Effective Communication&rdquo; are essentially half-price, this offer is good only for a limited time. <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135924&amp;ebr=179852044">So if you want in, get in now. </a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="bottom-nav" style="overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:10px;">\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135925&amp;ebr=179852044" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135926&amp;ebr=179852044" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=135927&amp;ebr=179852044" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n<