pan style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Welcome!</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></b></b></span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.15;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">It''s great to have you as part of The Suitcase Entrepreneur Community.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></b></b></span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.15;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">It can be incredibly rewarding building a business you love. There''s simply no better way to stay true to your purpose and create value for others, than living life on your own terms.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></b></b></span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.15;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Right now you&rsquo;re either on the verge of startup which is exciting and scary all at once, </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.15;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">or you have a business that you&rsquo;re wanting to scale but without losing sight of the freedom to do the things you love in life. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></b></b></span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.15;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Here&rsquo;s the good news; You do not have to go on this journey alone. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></b></b></span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.15;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">I am here to be your friend, your guide, your trusted advisor and coach, as you embark on creating your ideal lifestyle and discover the joys of working from anywhere.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"><b style="font-weight: normal;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></b></b></span>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="margin: 0; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; line-height: 1.15;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">And trust me, you need this as being an entreprene